    "date": "2025-09-03T15:37:57Z",
    "text": "Securities Research Modernization Act\n\nThis bill allows a securities broker or dealer to publish or distribute a research report on a proposed public offering by any issuer without it being considered an offer to sell securities for purposes of registration requirements. Currently, only reports published or distributed regarding a proposed public offering by an emerging growth company fall under this exception."
